    • isUsableForChangeExtraction

      public boolean isUsableForChangeExtraction()
      インタフェースからコピーされた説明: EntityType
      Returns whether or not ChangeDistiller should extract changes occurred on this source code entity type (e.g., changes in the finally clause are ignored).
      定義:
      isUsableForChangeExtraction インタフェース内 EntityType
      戻り値:
      true if ChangeDistiller should extract changes on this entity type, false otherwise.
